org.apache.hadoop.hbase.ipc

接口 CoprocessorRpcChannel

  • 所有超级接口:
    com.google.protobuf.BlockingRpcChannel, com.google.protobuf.RpcChannel

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
public interface CoprocessorRpcChannel
extends com.google.protobuf.RpcChannel, com.google.protobuf.BlockingRpcChannel
    Base interface which provides clients with an RPC connection to call coprocessor endpoint Services. Note that clients should not use this class directly, except through Table.coprocessorService(byte[]).
